"'''A Drunken Man's Praise of Sobriety'''" is a poem written by the [[Ireland|Irish]] poet [[William Butler Yeats]]. It is featured as a song on the bonus disk of [[Elvis Costello]]'s album [[Brutal Youth (Elvis Costello album)|Brutal Youth]].

